sc_cat_item.description:
Service Overview: Our Digital Prototype Accelerator equips organizations with rapid, customizable digital product prototypes that deliver HCLS services. Designed to advance from concept to prototype in just 15 minutes, our service streamlines the development process, enabling public sector organizations to focus on refinement and deployment.


Product Offerings:

  HCLS - Patient Support Services:

  • Flexible Patient Support Services data model
  • Workflows streamline tasks and offer end-to-end visibility to patient onboarding
  • Convenient, digital patient enrollment 
  • Training, knowledge, and checklists help to improve the end-to-end experience for all of the individuals involved.

 Key Advantages:

  1. Fast Time to Value: From initiation to prototype in 15 minutes.
  2. Configurability: Flexible solutions adaptable to specific agency needs.
  3. Integration Ready: Designed for easy integration with existing services.
  4. Secure and Compliant: Meets stringent government security and compliance standards.
